Definition list
   a list with several term-definition pairs in the form

   .. parsed-literal::

      **TERM**
         DEFINITION (*description of term*)

   Terms
      should not be indented

   Definitions
      should be indented under the term

Line spacing
   there should be a blank line between term-definition pairs

